==各項統計資料==
===住院===
根據{{link-en|醫療衛生成本和利用項目|Healthcare Cost and Utilization Project}}（HCUP，一項美國聯邦和業界合作的資料軟體工具/產品項目）的資料摘要，美國在2016年有3,570萬例的住院治療<ref name=":03">{{Cite web|url=https://www.hcup-us.ahrq.gov/reports/statbriefs/sb246-Geographic-Variation-Hospital-Stays.jsp|title=Overview of U.S. Hospital Stays in 2016: Variation by Geographic Region #246|website=www.hcup-us.ahrq.gov|access-date=2019-11-10|archive-date=2020-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200330201754/https://www.hcup-us.ahrq.gov/reports/statbriefs/sb246-Geographic-Variation-Hospital-Stays.jsp|dead-url=no}}</ref>，比2011年的3,860萬例顯著減少。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hcup-us.ahrq.gov/reports/statbriefs/sb166.jsp|title=Overview of Hospital Stays in the United States, 2011 - Statistical Brief #166|website=www.hcup-us.ahrq.gov|access-date=2019-11-10|archive-date=2020-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200330201756/https://www.hcup-us.ahrq.gov/reports/statbriefs/sb166.jsp|dead-url=no}}</ref>每 1,000人中，平均有104.2次住院治療，平均每次費用為11,700元 <ref name=":03" />，較2012年的每次費用10,400有所增加。<ref>{{cite book | vauthors = Weiss AJ, Elixhauser A | chapter = Overview of Hospital Stays in the United States, 2012: Statistical Brief #180 | date = 2006 | pmid = 25506966 | chapter-url = http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK259100/ | access-date = 2019-11-10 | publisher = Agency for Healthcare Research and Quality (US) | title = Healthcare Cost and Utilization Project (HCUP) Statistical Briefs }}</ref>2017年有7.6％的患者在醫院逗留，需要度過一晚<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cdc.gov/nchs/fastats/hospital.htm|title=FastStats|date=2019-09-04|website=www.cdc.gov|language=en-us|access-date=2019-11-10|archive-date=2020-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200330201757/https://www.cdc.gov/nchs/fastats/hospital.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，平均每次逗留 4.6天<ref name=":03" />。

NIH的一項研究報告說，使用2000年的美元作計算，美國人出生後的人均終生醫療衛生費用支出，女性為361,192美元，和男性的268,679美元，兩性間的費用間有不小的差異。這種差異的很大部分是由於男性的壽命較短，但是即使把年齡調整之後（假設男性的壽命與女性的壽命相同），終生醫療衛生支出仍有20％的差異。<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Alemayehu B, Warner KE | title = The lifetime distribution of health care costs | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_health-services-research_2004-06_39_3/page/627 | journal = Health Services Research | volume = 39 | issue = 3 | pages = 627–42 | date = June 2004 | pmid = 15149482 | pmc = 1361028 | doi = 10.1111/j.1475-6773.2004.00248.x }}</ref>
 
