{{link-en|美國州政府|State governments of the United States}}管理自己的{{link-en|州衛生部|state health agency}}，而地方政府（縣和市）通常也有衛生部門，多半是州衛生部的分支機構。州衛生部立下的法規具有行政和警察權力，可用以強制執行。在某些州，州衛生部的所有成員必須是醫事專業人員。州衛生部的成員可以由州長任命，或由州議會選舉產生。地方衛生部門的成員可由市長理事會選舉產生。麥卡倫–弗格森法案把監管權力交給各州，但是法案本身並不規範保險，也沒有要求州去規範保險。沒有明確意圖規範"保險業務"的"國會法案"去取代規範 "保險業務"的州法律或法規。麥卡倫–弗格森法案還規定，只要州在該領域進行監管，{{link-en|美國反托拉斯法|United States antitrust law}}對當地的"保險業務"就不適用，但是聯邦的反托拉斯法仍可透過抵制、脅迫、和恐嚇的方式達到效果。相比之下，無論州是否在其境內作監管，大多數其他聯邦法律都不適用在保險事務。<ref>{{cite book|last= |first= |date= |title= US Healthcare Sector - Organization, Management and Payment Systems Handbook|url= https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=1zbJCgAAQBAJ&pg=PA24&lpg=PA24&dq=The+McCarran%E2%80%93Ferguson+Act,+which+cedes+regulation+to+the+states,+does+not+itself+regulate+insurance,+nor+does+it+mandate+that+states+regulate+insurance.+%22Acts+of+Congress%22+that+do+not+expressly+purport+to+regulate+the+%22business+of+insurance%22+will+not+preempt+state+laws+or+regulations+that+regulate+the+%22business+of+insurance.%22+The+Act+also+provides+that+federal+anti-trust+laws+will+not+apply+to+the+%22business+of+insurance%22+as+long+as+the+state+regulates+in+that+area,+but+federal+anti-trust+laws+will+apply+in+cases+of+boycott,+coercion,+and+intimidation.+By+contrast,+most+other+federal+laws+will+not+apply+to+insurance+whether+the+states+regulate+in+that+area+or+not.&source=bl&ots=Jc6mpnI9is&sig=ACfU3U18zFkUfMovaxhAzz12rSSXfnqRvg&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwiViZnXnJHvAhUDE6YKHZJiAq4Q6AEwAHoECAUQAw#v=onepage&q=The%20McCarran%E2%80%93Ferguson%20Act%2C%20which%20cedes%20regulation%20to%20the%20states%2C%20does%20not%20itself%20regulate%20insurance%2C%20nor%20does%20it%20mandate%20that%20states%20regulate%20insurance.%20%22Acts%20of%20Congress%22%20that%20do%20not%20expressly%20purport%20to%20regulate%20the%20%22business%20of%20insurance%22%20will%20not%20preempt%20state%20laws%20or%20regulations%20that%20regulate%20the%20%22business%20of%20insurance.%22%20The%20Act%20also%20provides%20that%20federal%