====人口統計差異====
{{main|{{link-en|美國的種族與健康|Race and health in the United States}}|{{link-en|美國的貧窮與健康|Poverty and health in the United States}}}}
[[File:CDC_TB_graphic_on_minority_groups_being_impacted_by_TB.jpg|thumb]]在美國不同族裔間醫療衛生不平等的情況。]]
 
在美國，[[少數群體|少數族裔]]如[[非裔美國人|非裔美國人]]、[[美國原住民|美國原住民]]、和[[拉丁裔美國人|拉丁裔美國人]]，他們的健康差異有詳實的記載。<ref>Goldberg, J., Hayes, W., and Huntley, J. [http://www.healthpolicyohio.org/publications/healthdisparities.html "Understanding Health Disparities."] {{Wayback|url=http://www.healthpolicyohio.org/publications/healthdisparities.html |date=20080515210412 }} Health Policy Institute of Ohio (November 2004), p. 3.</ref>與[[美國白人|美國白人]]相比，這些群體有更高的慢性病發病率、更高的死亡率、以及更差的健康結果。在特定疾病的種族和族裔差異例子中，非裔美國人的癌症發病率比白人高25％。<ref name="APHA">American Public Health Association (APHA), Eliminating Health Disparities: Toolkit (2004).</ref>此外，成年的非裔美國人和拉丁裔美國人罹患患糖尿病的風險大約是白人的兩倍，並且他們的肥胖症比白人高。<ref>{{cite web |last=Campanile |first=Carl |name-list-format=vanc |url=http://www.nypost.com/p/news/national/we_regoing_wide_UBV52r2Rl9hejdZDaGTgNM |title=Americans are getting fatter: poll |publisher=New York Post |website=Nypost.com |date=2012-11-23 |access-date=2016-12-01 |archive-date=2013-07-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130703120942/http://www.nypost.com/p/news/national/we_regoing_wide_UBV52r2Rl9hejdZDaGTgNM |dead-url=no }}</ref>少數族裔罹患心血管疾病和[[愛滋病|愛滋病]]的比率也高過白人。<ref name="APHA" />[[亞裔美國人|亞裔美國人]]的壽命最長（87.1歲），其次是拉丁裔（83.3歲），白人（78.9歲），美國原住民（76.9歲），和排在尾巴的非裔（75.4歲）。<ref>Sarah Burd-Sharps and Kristen Lewis. ''[http://www.measureofamerica.org/congressional-districts-2015/ Geographies of Opportunity: Ranking Well-Being by Congressional District] {{Wayback|url=http://www.measureofamerica.org/congressional-districts-2015/ |date=20180102003310 }}''. 2015. [[Measure_of_America|Measure of America]] of  the Social Science Research Council.</ref>2001年所做的一項研究發現，在較低的教育水準人群中，種族間的健康預期壽命存有很大的差異。<ref>''[http://cat.inist.fr/?aModele=afficheN&cpsidt=1050427 Trends in healthy life expectancy in the united states, 1970–1990 : gender, racial, and educational differences] {{Wayback|url=http://cat.inist.fr/?aModele=afficheN&cpsidt=1050427 |date=20100317145539 }}''</ref>
 
公共支出與年齡有高度的關聯性；花在老年人身上的的人均公共支出是兒童的五倍多（分別為6,921美元和1,225美元）。花在美國非西班牙裔黑人（母語為英語的黑人）的人均公共支出（2,973美元）略高於白人（2,675美元），而花在[[西班牙裔|西班牙裔]]的公共支出（1,967美元）顯著低於人口平均水平（2,612美元）。公共支出總額也與自我報告的健康狀況密切相關（自我報告健康狀況欠佳的人為13,770美元，報告健康狀況良好的人為1,279美元）。<ref name="content.healthaffairs.org" />老年人佔人口的13％，但用掉所有處方藥的三分之一。老年人平均每年要用掉38張處方箋。<ref>{{cite news | first=Pamela | last=Tronetti | name-list-format = vanc | title=Senior consult:Check drugs supplements to avoid interactions | url=http://www.floridatoday.com/article/20110111/LIFE01/101110310/Dr-Pamela-TronettiI-Check-drugs-supplements-to-avoid-interactions| newspaper=Florida Today | location=Melbourne, Florida | page= 1D | date=2011-01-11 }}</ref>一項新的研究還發現，雖然沒證據表明南方的老年人中有更多需要用[[抗細菌藥|抗生素]]治療的疾病，但南方的老年人比其他地方的更經常使用抗生素。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://well.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/09/25/antibiotic-prescription-it-may-depend-on-where-you-live/?partner=rss&emc=rss |title=Well: Antibiotic Prescription? It May Depend on Where You Live |work=The New York Times |first=Anahad |last=O'Connor |name-list-format=vanc |date=2012-09-25 |accessdate=2020-09-04 |archive-date=2020-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201028060051/https://well.blogs.nytimes.com/2012/09/25/antibiotic-prescription-it-may-depend-on-where-you-live/?partner=rss&emc=rss |dead-url=no }}</ref>
 
關於針對醫療衛生不平等的研究很多。但是在某些情況下，這些不平等是由於收入差距所造成，這樣的差距是由於缺乏醫療保險，還有接受服務的障礙所造成。<ref>[http://www.kff.org/uninsured/7705.cfm "How Trends in the Health Care System Affect Low-Income Adults: Identifying Access Problems and Financial Burdens"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.kff.org/uninsured/7705.cfm |date=20130120065551 }}, Issue Brief: Kaiser Commission on Medicaid and the Uninsured, December 21, 2007. Retrieved February 26, 2008.</ref>根據2009年國家醫療衛生品質與差異報告（National Healthcare Quality and Disparities Reports），未投保的美國人接受預防醫學服務的可能性較小。<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Habib JL | year = 2010 | title = Progress lags in infection prevention and health disparities | url = http://dbt.consultantlive.com/display/article/1145628/1582744 | journal = Drug Benefit Trends | volume = 22 | issue = 4 | page = 112 | access-date = 2020-09-04 | archive-date = 2013-01-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130120065516/http://dbt.consultantlive.com/display/article/1145628/1582744 | dead-url = no }}</ref>例如，少數族裔沒定期接受大腸癌篩檢，非裔美國人和西班牙裔人中因大腸癌的死亡率呈上升趨勢。在其他情況下，醫療衛生的不平等現象，反映出針對不同族裔所給予的醫療程序和治療上的系統性偏見。[[愛丁堡大學|愛丁堡大學]]教授拉傑·博帕爾（Raj Bhopal）寫道，[[科學種族主義|科學種族主義]]和醫學種族主義的歷史清楚的顯示，無論是人和機構，都按照他們的時代精神行事。<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Bhopal R | title = Spectre of racism in health and health care: lessons from history and the United States | journal = BMJ | volume = 316 | issue = 7149 | pages = 1970–3 | date = June 1998 | pmid = 9641943 | pmc = 1113412 | doi = 10.1136/bmj.316.7149.1970 }}</ref>{{link-en|南希·克里格|Nancy Krieger}}寫道，種族主義是醫療服務中難以解釋的不平等現象的基礎，其中包括治療心臟病、<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Oberman A, Cutter G | title = Issues in the natural history and treatment of coronary heart disease in black populations: surgical treatment | journal = American Heart Journal | volume = 108 | issue = 3 Pt 2 | pages = 688–94 | date = September 1984 | pmid = 6332513 | doi = 10.1016/0002-8703(84)90656-2 }}</ref> [[腎功能衰竭|腎功能衰竭]]、<ref name="pmid3288159">{{cite journal | vauthors = Kjellstrand CM | title = Age, sex, and race inequality in renal transplantation | journal = Archives of Internal Medicine | volume = 148 | issue = 6 | pages = 1305–9 | date = June 1988 | pmid = 3288159 | doi = 10.1001/archinte.1988.00380060069016 }}</ref> [[膀胱癌|膀胱癌]]、<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Mayer WJ, McWhorter WP | title = Black/white differences in non-treatment of bladder cancer patients and implications for survival | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_american-journal-of-public-health_1989-06_79_6/page/772 | journal = American Journal of Public Health | volume = 79 | issue = 6 | pages = 772–5 | date = June 1989 | pmid = 2729474 | pmc = 1349641 | doi = 10.2105/ajph.79.6.772 }}</ref>、還有[[肺炎|肺炎]]。<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Yergan J, Flood AB, LoGerfo JP, Diehr P | title = Relationship between patient race and the intensity of hospital services | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_medical-care_1987-07_25_7/page/592 | journal = Medical Care | volume = 25 | issue = 7 | pages = 592–603 | date = July 1987 | pmid = 3695664 | doi = 10.1097/00005650-198707000-00003 | s2cid = 11637921 }}</ref> 拉傑·博帕爾寫道，這些不平等現像散見於不少研究之中。持續的和重複的發現是非裔美國人比白人獲得較少的醫療衛生服務，尤其是涉及到昂貴新技術的時候。<ref name="#2">{{cite journal | title = Black-white disparities in health care | journal = JAMA | volume = 263 | issue = 17 | pages = 2344–6 | date = May 1990 | pmid = 2182918 | doi = 10.1001/jama.263.17.2344 | author1 = Council on Ethical Judicial Affairs }}</ref>最近的一項研究則發現，當少數族裔和白人患者同時在同一家醫院時，他們會獲得相同水準的護理。<ref name="#2"/>

